  <annotations>
    <annotation>
      <subheading>About This Website</subheading>
      <text><a href="/">codes.baltimorecity.gov</a> is the official home for the laws, regulations, and administrative policies of the <a href="https://www.baltimorecity.gov/">City of Baltimore</a>. It is edited and published by the <a href="https://www.baltimorecity.gov/legislative-reference">Department of Legislative Reference</a>.</text>
      <text>This site makes City law easier to search, browse, and cite, allowing visitors to find what they need without knowing in advance where it lives.</text>
      <text>For pending legislation and upcoming City Council meetings, the Council maintains its official legislative information system at <a href="https://baltimore.legistar.com/">baltimore.legistar.com</a>.</text>
    </annotation>
